Signed-off-by: Jani Nikula <jani.nikula@intel.com>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/db8952baa3e3e5eaaa8a3a5bc723c4e47aeaa6a7.1740564009.git.jani.nikula@intel.com
